    "Moreover, we showcase the effectiveness of CAPA over the original Prompt Adapter (PA).Effectiveness of High-Fidelity Mask Decoder.",
    "As shown in Tab.",
    "5, using HFMD brings significant performance gains over merely fine-tuning SAM on target datasets.",
    "Specifically, compared to SAM-FineTune, incorporating HFMD improves 11.4% mIoU and 14.5% mBIoU on ELE-40K, 4.7% mIoU and 5.4% mBIoU on HQSeg-44K.",
    "Moreover, while comparing HFMD with HFMD (w/o HR) on both datasets, we observe that introducing high-resolution mask features also improves the segmentation results from low-resolution mask features."
